Chinese State to Buy Portugal Bailout Bond, EFSF Says, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-26T00:23:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/chinese-state-to-buy-portugal-bailout-bond-efsf-says-ft-says.html
European Financial Stability Facility
Chief Executive Officer Klaus Regling said Asian investors,
including the Chinese government, may comprise a “strong
proportion” of the purchasers of Portuguese bailout bonds when
the EFSF begins selling them in June, the Financial Times
reported, citing remarks by Regling to reporters yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
